item.title: How To read How To Win Friends and Influence People
item.description:
How To read How To Win Friends and Influence People

Reading How To Win Friends and Influence People is like rereading the cover letter of an essay just before you hand it in. You're pretty sure that you did everything, but when you check back it's clear that somewhere along the line, you and it lost touch. And you hope desperately that won't make much of a difference.
